，仲有你嘅摯愛，簽名？刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\nPostal Code 請填000000，如果身處英國就填所在地點嘅Code<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmobsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=064fdffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"}]}